      "name": "Generic baseline",
      "description": "Minimal Xentral system configuration that fits any business\nmodel. Use this when the model isn't yet decided or as a\nstarting point that you specialise after first orders are\nflowing. All defaults are conservative — no marketplaces, no\nnewsletter, no advanced returns workflow. Activate modules\nas the business grows.\n",
